                            Alumni Loyalty and Benefits Committee
                    








            Alumni Loyalty and Benefits Committee
          

Alumni Loyalty and Benefits Committee
The Alumni Loyalty and Benefits Committee works to advise on alumni loyalty programs/opportunities and reviews the value of benefits offered to Alumni.
Members
John Ochoa BArch ’78, *Committee Chair
